overview: Fanclub event DVD featuring Takahashi Ai, Michishige Sayumi, and Mitsui Aika It features their 2010 solo bus tour that ran from November 6th through 7th 2010 in Yamanashi. Disc 1 (81mins), Disc 2 (59mins).
